The '''Darkwoods Massacre''' was a battle fought in the [[Darkwoods]] of [[Cormanthor]] between an [[orc]] horde from [[Vastar]] and combined [[elf|elven]] and [[human]] forces of the [[Akh'Velahr]] of [[Cormanthyr]] in [[335 DR|the Year of Seven Stones, 335 DR]].
